{"tid":1523304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[glock彈殼代表d咩］推到警察承認，一定追究！！","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T18:23:21.000Z","uid":232841,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd400a014eb693025002b63ab66140d18a7e003","tid":1523304,"uid":232841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5htQShU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5htQShU.png&h=6584c416&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgSqGbi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgSqGbi.png&h=78b3fdfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢粒彈殼唔係平時警察用開既左輪，而係高一級既glock半自動手槍<br />\n第二張相已經睇到依家警察偷偷用「便衣」開槍等我地追究唔到！<br />\n<br />\nGlock 半自動手槍 vs 左輪？<br />\n1）同樣嘅子彈，因為Glock嘅槍管長d，旋轉比大d，槍膛密封性好d，子彈初速會更高<br />\n<br />\n2）警察軍裝左輪係用. 45 acp子彈，子彈口徑大d，初速比Glock 17用嘅9mm低。<br />\n<br />\n3）軍裝用嘅左輪手槍，有效射程係50米內，而Glock 17，好多外國shooter喺200米左右都仍然可以精確射擊人形鋼靶<br />\n<br />\n4）Glock 17載彈量有17發，相比起左輪嘅6發，連續射擊嘅能力都強好多<br />\n<br />\n5）半自動手槍嘅設計，後助力嘅力距亦比左輪手槍更細，射擊時導致槍口上提嘅後助力都更細，更好控制<br />\n<br />\n姐係點呀？ 姐係依家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擺明車馬要用便衣殺死人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推！推到警察承認！一定要算帳！</span>"},{"pid":"d20f5166649cd7eb4925c1e681fc0a41c003d574","tid":1523304,"uid":273466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vKwBOd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vKwBOd.jpg&h=c135976a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKRrqGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKRrqGy.jpg&h=1b735665&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BaiA3td.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBaiA3td.jpg&h=fe1b114a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnYM98e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https